root: ^We can see there is more than just strings as well. Integers, decimals, and boolean values are also used in everything you will do!
^Integers represent your typical whole numbers, and decimals are anything that isn't.
^Boolean values you may no have heard of... they are used to determine if something is simply true or false!
^Now, since you clearly know what you are doing, try and figure out what these ones do too.
